The IHC Group understands that your time is precious, and you may not want to spend hours researching health insurance plans. 
      So we've made it simple.  Our innovative online quoting tools give you an array of products to choose from, at various price 
      points to fit your lifestyle and budget. Take a few minutes, not a few hours, to find the health insurance plan that is right 
      for you.
      
Shop now  


Short-term medical – temporary health insurance for 30 days to 11 months



Dental – low cost dental insurance for preventative care, treatment and services


Premier - bundled critical illness, accident, life and disability insurance


Individual – major medical coverage and affordable hospital and surgical indemnity plans


Prescription – no health questions, drug card program


Pet insurance – veterinary, wellness, cancer and accident coverage for domestic dogs or cats


Have an insurance producer contact me 



