Who is The IHC Group?
The IHC Group is an organization of insurance carriers, and marketing and administrative affiliates that has been providing life, health, disability, dental, and vision insurance solutions to groups and individuals for over 30 years. 
      
Members of The IHC Group include Independence Holding Company (NYSE:IHC), Standard Security Life Insurance Company of New York, Madison National Life Insurance Company, Inc.,  Independence American Insurance Company and IHC Specialty Benefits.
      
Meet Our Leadership Team



